	   <tr><td colspan=2>As they stated, Bearskin can be easily sold for platinum to get Banded. I have tried this theory, here is what I did with my newbie ranger:<br>Quested for the Gloves<br>Sold Gloves and Bought Banded Gloves and Leggings<br>Quested for the Gloves AGAIN<br>Sold Gloves and Bought Banded BP and Arms<br>Quested for Gloves AGAIN<br>Sold Gloves and Bought Banded Bracers and Boots<br>Quested for Gloves AGAIN<br>Sold Gloves and Bought Banded Helm, Collar and Mask<br>Quested for Gloves AGAIN<br>Sold Gloves and Bought Banded Cape, Girdle and Mantle<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>I found myself in good shape, not having to spend any money on my twink and have good AC and basic Stats.<br>I decided to quest 3 more times, and with the money I bought 2 Cutthroat Igisna Rings and 2 Diamondine Earrings<br>--------------------------------------------------Now he is level 12, wielding a mainhand FS Long Sword and a FS rapier in his offhand.<br><br>He has quested lots and made a big profit and bought some Ivy Etched Armor, and I must tell you. Playing this ranger and questing for these gloves, meeting new people, talking and having the excitement of getting this for my twink...<br><br>...It was just plain out fun. It reminded me of my old newbie days. I helped out people by giving some out and made Greater Faydark a better place.<br><br>I experienced tons of fights and stopped them, and helped lots of people.<br>--------------------------------------------------Not only can you make a good profit off of these and get lots of banded and 2 good weapons (better then mine, hehe), you can have fun doing it.<br><br>At the time my ranger got the bearskin, I went along with people and we talked, so not only is this a profitable experience, it can be fun too.<br><br>So, to all you level 5-12s, do this quest, have some fun and get some good armor!<br><br>Good Luck, I hope you liked my little experience with this quest, and even better experiences will happen to you!<br><br>-Boombaa Shadowslayer<br>11KPP of Items gaven away on the Innoruuk Server in 3 months, and is proud of it.<br>&nbsp;<br>Boombaa Shadowslayer<br>51st Ogre Warrior<br><br>Hierophantt<br>10th Iksar Monk<br><br>Tenamin<br>10th Half Elf Pa</td></tr>
